            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">The Pragmatist</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">You want to automate the boring parts of your work or life. You care about results, not hype.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
