          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">The Learner</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">You are tired of theoretical "thought leadership" and want practical "how-to" knowledge.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-rose-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-rose-600">
